          <h2>_</h2>
          <br>
          <p>
            A computer vision algorithm together with a camera identifies the object presented to the tap.
            Tappy then uses a closed loop control system to learn and adjust the taps water delivery based on feedback from use of the tap.
            All these components are housed and connected by 3D-printed parts.
          </p>


